01:25:44.388 --> 01:25:49.280
We've tried to find people's eyes that look like Eve's eyes.

01:25:49.280 --> 01:25:54.000
I said, "If I ever find them, Diana, I'll show you.

01:25:54.000 --> 01:26:04.116
" They looked almost a greenish color with a mixture of brown and a little blue in them.

01:26:04.116 --> 01:26:06.500
Explain that—it was beautiful, the eye.

01:26:20.939 --> 01:26:21.159
I didn't see Adam's eyes, but Eve was sitting down with her hair around her.

01:26:21.159 --> 01:26:35.063
I saw her sitting on a little rock with ferns growing around her, and she was doing something, but it happened quickly.

01:26:35.063 --> 01:26:42.253
I was thinking, "What in the world?

01:26:42.253 --> 01:26:45.360
" Everything in the garden at that moment was glorious.

01:26:45.360 --> 01:26:52.739
It was beautiful going back and being able to see that again.

01:26:52.739 --> 01:27:00.582
Birds were the size of cars; they were truly massive.

01:27:16.159 --> 01:27:16.773
It was prehistoric.

01:27:18.000 --> 01:27:19.679
It was beautiful.

01:27:19.679 --> 01:27:21.813
Things weren't like now.

01:27:21.813 --> 01:27:26.900
Things were bigger: the trees were bigger, the plants were bigger.

01:27:26.900 --> 01:27:31.024
So, is that enough?

01:27:37.466 --> 01:27:37.724
I don't know if I answered that right.

01:27:37.724 --> 01:27:41.860
But I could see the pyramids; I could see everything being constructed.

01:27:45.390 --> 01:27:56.752
I think people think there are conspiracies happening, which is why they are asking about conspiracies—how it was built.

01:28:14.297 --> 01:28:14.708
I saw men building them.

01:28:20.480 --> 01:28:23.780
I didn't see aliens building the pyramids.

01:28:23.780 --> 01:28:32.020
They were men building the pyramids, and they had wooden things.

01:28:32.020 --> 01:28:36.930
They were dragging things around.

01:28:36.930 --> 01:28:39.520
People ask, "How'd that happen?

01:28:39.520 --> 01:28:45.270
" There were literally hundreds, if not thousands, of men moving these things around.

01:28:51.199 --> 01:28:52.755
I could see all these ramps and all this stuff being moved around.

01:28:52.755 --> 01:29:01.543
People say, "Well, how'd they lift a big stone like that?

01:29:01.543 --> 01:29:02.536
" They did.

01:29:02.536 --> 01:29:05.485
But there were bigger men.

01:29:05.485 --> 01:29:12.622
Now, if those were giants, I don't know, but it was happening quickly and panning out before my face.

01:29:12.764 --> 01:29:16.080
It was happening so fast that it was moving like this, and I was trying to glimpse it.

01:29:16.080 --> 01:29:32.560
I was looking at the Chinese Empire and all the things going on with the Great Wall of China; it was all being constructed right in front of my face.

01:29:32.560 --> 01:29:43.459
The Lord was just showing me things about time.

01:29:51.670 --> 01:29:51.920
And the city of Atlantis was out by Africa.

01:29:56.539 --> 01:29:56.729
It was an actual city.

01:29:59.920 --> 01:30:00.160
I saw it being swallowed up by fire and water.

01:30:00.160 --> 01:30:05.631
As it was playing out for me, I knew what it was.

01:30:06.495 --> 01:30:08.719
The Lord said to me, "This is the lost city of Atlantis.

01:30:08.719 --> 01:30:11.140
" It was a mass—not just a little town.

01:30:11.140 --> 01:30:21.500
We're talking a massive thing, almost like an island, and it was destroyed.

01:30:29.636 --> 01:30:29.935
I could see the storm.

01:30:29.935 --> 01:30:31.724
I could see lightning.

01:30:37.779 --> 01:30:37.969
I could see things.

01:30:37.969 --> 01:30:41.760
There was something that happened.

01:30:41.760 --> 01:30:43.378
Brandon, that's way out there.

01:30:43.609 --> 01:31:03.280
A lot of things I don't share, because people—that's why I say if I can't usually back it up in scripture or whatever, I don't talk about a lot of things.

01:31:12.765 --> 01:31:12.941
But tonight I thought, well, I didn't have a lot.

01:31:12.941 --> 01:31:20.220
But I'll tell you some of the things I've seen and it's kind of interesting.

01:31:20.220 --> 01:31:28.124
I just keep a lot of things to myself.

01:31:50.048 --> 01:31:50.360
I just go, 'Well, you know, it's way out there.

01:31:50.360 --> 01:31:52.960
Are people going to believe it?

01:31:52.960 --> 01:31:57.140
' Well, there were dinosaurs, folks, and they were walking around Adam.

01:31:57.140 --> 01:32:07.320
It was a massive looking long-neck dinosaur, and he was talking to it, and it understood him as it was eating the trees.

01:32:22.287 --> 01:32:22.591
And Adam was talking to this thing.

01:32:22.591 --> 01:32:28.133
I don't know how it was like—did he speak dinosaur?

01:32:32.060 --> 01:32:32.450
I have no idea.

01:32:54.239 --> 01:32:54.426
But the dinosaur, like we talk to dogs and they listen to us, animals were listening to him.

01:33:00.040 --> 01:33:00.260
And that's why I was like, 'Look at that.

01:33:00.260 --> 01:33:15.333
' That big old long-neck dinosaur looks like one of those brachiosauruses that you know, like those long-neck dinosaurs on Jurassic Park.

01:33:18.516 --> 01:33:18.773
It was huge.

01:33:18.773 --> 01:33:24.639
It looked like a thunder lizard, a massive lizard, but I don't know.

01:33:24.639 --> 01:33:28.149
Father, we just thank you, Lord, for the body.

01:33:28.149 --> 01:33:32.746
Thank you, Lord, for all that you've done for us.

01:33:32.746 --> 01:33:35.424
Lord, you're so good to us.

01:33:52.275 --> 01:33:52.824
And Father, we don't take anything that you've done for granted.

01:33:52.824 --> 01:33:53.921
Nothing.

01:33:54.480 --> 01:34:26.320
And where we are in this dispensation of grace, where we are in this timeframe, Father, that you said Brandon, Diana, Brad, all of us come to this earth for such a time as this, that we were the closers.

01:34:28.780 --> 01:34:29.040
And you said, 'I've saved the best for last.

01:34:29.040 --> 01:34:32.320
All of you are saved the best for last.

01:34:32.320 --> 01:34:36.280
' You're my closers, every single one of us.

01:34:37.420 --> 01:34:44.668
I believe that this is the generation that will not taste death.

01:34:44.668 --> 01:34:52.746
And Father, I thank you for your body.

01:34:52.746 --> 01:34:54.764
This is what did it all.

01:35:08.251 --> 01:35:08.674
You paid the price for us to walk in victory.

01:35:16.719 --> 01:35:16.999
You paid the price for us to walk in healing.

01:35:18.960 --> 01:35:21.339
You paid the price for us to walk in deliverance.

01:35:21.939 --> 01:35:28.309
You paid the price for Diana and me, my children, and for all those that are watching.

01:35:28.309 --> 01:35:34.800
Father, for those that will continue to watch in the days, we pray for everyone in the world.

01:35:34.800 --> 01:35:36.900
You paid the price.

01:35:36.900 --> 01:35:38.445
Thank you, Lord.

01:35:38.445 --> 01:35:45.680
As we enter into this time of thanksgiving, as we enter into this time, we're so grateful.

01:35:45.680 --> 01:35:46.400
Thank you, Lord.

01:35:46.400 --> 01:35:49.013
We take this body right now in the name of Jesus.

01:35:49.013 --> 01:35:51.657
And we thank you, Lord, that we see that which is to come.

01:35:51.657 --> 01:35:58.949
Father, if there's anything you want us to see, let us have eyes to see and ears to hear what the spirit is saying.

01:35:58.949 --> 01:36:04.480
We take this body right now in Jesus' name.

01:36:04.720 --> 01:36:07.180
The anointing just hit my left hand.

01:36:07.180 --> 01:36:08.959
It's not the right hand.

01:36:08.959 --> 01:36:11.508
It's going to be this hand.

01:36:11.508 --> 01:36:16.920
I felt the Holy Ghost and fire hit all the way down to my elbow.

01:36:16.920 --> 01:36:18.213
That is very interesting.

01:36:18.213 --> 01:36:21.760
When I was holding the body, thank you Lord.

01:36:21.760 --> 01:36:24.224
Hallelujah.

01:36:24.224 --> 01:36:28.592
Diana, you believe for anything?

01:36:36.160 --> 01:36:36.500
I bless you in Jesus' name.

01:36:36.500 --> 01:36:45.190
Father, I thank you Lord for my wife healed and whole and well and filled with the power of God in Jesus' name.

01:36:52.730 --> 01:36:53.060
I feel if it's there, it's there for a reason.

01:36:53.060 --> 01:36:55.298
He doesn't just do that.

01:36:55.298 --> 01:37:00.240
Thank you Lord for the blood in Jesus' name.

01:37:00.240 --> 01:37:04.719
I'm actually feeling like I'm getting drunk in the Holy Ghost.

01:37:04.719 --> 01:37:05.479
That is amazing.

01:37:05.479 --> 01:37:05.859
Hallelujah.

01:37:05.859 --> 01:37:06.239
Wow.

01:37:06.239 --> 01:37:06.879
Hallelujah.

01:37:06.879 --> 01:37:07.520
Hallelujah.

01:37:07.520 --> 01:37:08.160
Wow.

01:37:08.160 --> 01:37:09.760
My tongue got it.

01:37:09.760 --> 01:37:11.626
Oh my goodness, Lord.

01:37:11.626 --> 01:37:15.693
Well, thank you, being filled with the Holy Ghost.

01:37:15.693 --> 01:37:18.040
Thank you, Lord, for the blood.

01:37:18.040 --> 01:37:27.471
Thank you, Father, that we make much of the blood and the blood makes much of us.

01:37:27.471 --> 01:37:29.377
Thank you for the blood.

01:37:29.377 --> 01:37:29.946
Hallelujah.

01:37:29.946 --> 01:37:30.515
Hallelujah.

01:37:30.515 --> 01:37:31.688
Glory to God.

01:37:31.688 --> 01:37:32.872
Thank you, Jesus.

01:37:32.872 --> 01:37:34.1000
We take the blood today.

01:37:34.1000 --> 01:37:37.439
We apply the blood over Diana, Braden, Megan Paisley, and me.

01:37:37.439 --> 01:37:40.639
I apply the blood.

01:37:40.639 --> 01:37:45.970
Where we make much of the blood, the blood makes much of us.

01:37:45.970 --> 01:37:49.634
We put angels all around and about us.

01:37:49.634 --> 01:37:52.797
Father, I thank you, Lord.

01:37:52.797 --> 01:38:00.192
Though we make much of the blood, we take the blood right now, Father.

01:38:00.192 --> 01:38:09.119
We thank you, Lord, that you forgive us of our sins in the name of Jesus.

01:38:09.119 --> 01:38:11.040
Amen and amen.

01:38:17.290 --> 01:38:17.720
You want a drink, baby?

01:38:17.720 --> 01:38:18.150
Thank you.

01:38:18.150 --> 01:38:19.840
Thank you, Lord.

01:38:19.840 --> 01:38:23.040
What can wash away my sin?

01:38:23.040 --> 01:38:25.027
Nothing but the blood of Jesus.

01:38:25.027 --> 01:38:28.800
Oh Father, fill our cup, Lord.

01:38:28.800 --> 01:38:31.589
We lift it up, Lord.

01:38:31.589 --> 01:38:34.971
Come and quench this thirsting of our soul.

01:38:34.971 --> 01:38:38.639
Bread of heaven, feed me till I want no more.

01:38:38.639 --> 01:38:42.786
Fill my cup, fill it up and make me whole.

01:38:42.786 --> 01:38:44.500
Fill our cup, Lord.

01:39:02.560 --> 01:39:02.800
I lift it up, Lord.

01:39:02.800 --> 01:39:07.308
Come and quench this thirsting of my soul.

01:39:07.308 --> 01:39:17.250
Bread of heaven, feed me till I want no more.

01:39:17.250 --> 01:39:19.050
Fill my cup.

01:39:19.050 --> 01:39:22.000
Fill it up and make me whole.

01:39:22.000 --> 01:39:22.832
Thank you, Lord.

01:39:22.832 --> 01:39:24.080
Fill our cup, Lord.

01:39:35.360 --> 01:39:35.707
I lift it up, Lord.

01:39:35.707 --> 01:39:39.166
Come and quench this thirsting of our soul.

01:39:39.166 --> 01:39:43.973
Bread of heaven, feed me till I want no more.

01:39:43.973 --> 01:39:45.467
Fill our cup.

01:39:45.467 --> 01:39:49.480
Fill it up and make me whole.

01:39:59.380 --> 01:40:05.199
I wish in the natural I could draw the pictures of what I saw, even about the pyramids and the things that I saw, the way the people looked as they were building things.

01:40:24.192 --> 01:40:24.616
The things that I have inside of me are such treasures.

01:40:24.616 --> 01:40:27.538
I could share them with everyone.

01:40:27.538 --> 01:40:31.939
How beautiful life is for all of us and we don't know it.

01:40:31.939 --> 01:40:36.191
Life is but a vapor and it moves so quickly.

01:40:36.191 --> 01:40:37.782
It's just a blink.

01:40:37.782 --> 01:40:42.217
What do we do with the blink we have?

01:40:59.520 --> 01:40:59.800
What do we do with the blink God's given us?

01:41:21.271 --> 01:41:21.600
It goes so quickly.

01:41:21.600 --> 01:41:38.102
What do we do with the relationship that he wants to have with every one of us?

01:41:38.102 --> 01:41:39.479
Life is a blink.

01:41:39.479 --> 01:41:41.062
Blink twice and it's over.

01:41:41.062 --> 01:41:46.378
Jesus, let us do something great in that blink.

01:41:46.378 --> 01:41:48.719
Oh Father, I thank you Lord.

01:42:10.373 --> 01:42:10.800
Every one of us has something that God's called us to do.

01:42:36.159 --> 01:42:36.409
We do it with all our heart.

01:42:36.409 --> 01:42:39.211
Oh Lord, I thank you for your relationship.

01:42:39.211 --> 01:42:40.857
Oh Lord, you're beautiful.

01:42:40.857 --> 01:42:43.160
Your face is all I seek.

01:42:43.740 --> 01:42:52.399
And when your eyes are on this child, your grace abounds to me.

01:42:52.399 --> 01:42:54.663
Oh Lord, you're beautiful.

01:42:54.663 --> 01:42:59.280
Your face is all I see.

01:42:59.280 --> 01:43:01.394
Thank you, Father.

01:43:15.920 --> 01:43:16.400
There's so many of you that just need refreshed.

01:43:16.400 --> 01:43:19.280
He said he'll bring the refreshing.

01:43:19.280 --> 01:43:20.933
He'll bring the rain.

01:43:20.933 --> 01:43:22.491
He'll bring the rain on you.

01:43:22.491 --> 01:43:25.440
He'll bring the rain.

01:43:29.069 --> 01:43:29.419
It's like I had last night.

01:43:29.769 --> 01:43:33.653
I sat there and said, 'Lord, bring the rain.

01:43:33.653 --> 01:43:35.576
Jesus, I am thirsty.

01:43:46.994 --> 01:43:47.336
I've poured out, Lord, and I need a fresh touch.

01:43:47.336 --> 01:43:50.068
' All you need is a drink.

01:43:50.068 --> 01:43:54.194
There's so many people here tonight that just need a drink.

01:43:54.194 --> 01:43:59.733
They just want things to be so real instead of false religion or just cookie-cutter.

01:43:59.733 --> 01:44:00.587
It's cookie-cutter.

01:44:15.600 --> 01:44:16.320
I don't say false religion, but just this Pharisaic religion.

01:44:24.159 --> 01:44:24.799
Jesus wants to become real to you.

01:44:31.191 --> 01:44:37.379
The Holy Spirit wants to become real to you.

01:44:37.379 --> 01:44:38.770
He's not a dove.

01:44:38.770 --> 01:44:40.510
He's not a feeling.

01:44:46.480 --> 01:44:47.013
He is a person.

01:45:07.860 --> 01:45:14.190
And he is more real to me than Diana is.

01:45:14.190 --> 01:45:27.477
I'm telling you, when he appeared and I was able to see him for the glimpse that I had, he's green.

01:45:38.479 --> 01:45:38.719
He's beautiful.

01:45:42.400 --> 01:45:42.651
He's alive.

01:45:43.154 --> 01:45:46.848
That probably just wrecked some people's world.

01:45:46.848 --> 01:45:53.008
But as I saw it, he's an all-consuming fire, but he's green.

01:45:53.008 --> 01:45:55.600
It's like blue fire.

01:45:55.600 --> 01:46:01.659
An all-consuming fire that's blue but just has a green tint to it.

01:46:05.700 --> 01:46:05.920
The Holy Spirit has a form and he's barrel-chested.

01:46:05.920 --> 01:46:06.880
He's huge.

01:46:06.880 --> 01:46:10.194
I'm talking like a thick barrel-chested man.

01:46:11.771 --> 01:46:13.554
The Holy Spirit is not skinny.

01:46:13.554 --> 01:46:14.667
He's barrel-chested.

01:46:25.949 --> 01:46:26.159
He looks like he has a 50-gallon wood barrel.

01:46:26.159 --> 01:46:28.773
That's how thick his chest is.

01:46:28.773 --> 01:46:37.680
I was allowed to see these glimpses when he came and talked to me one day and I said, 'Oh, it's nothing what I thought.

01:46:37.680 --> 01:46:38.740
He's massive.

01:46:38.740 --> 01:46:44.469
' But he wants to become more so real to you.

01:46:44.469 --> 01:46:45.634
Oh Jesus.

01:46:45.634 --> 01:46:50.697
People want to know, 'Brandon, how do you have these experiences?

01:46:50.697 --> 01:46:55.227
' But every single one of them is so dear to me.

01:46:55.227 --> 01:46:58.319
I'll never forget any of them.

01:46:58.319 --> 01:47:09.510
It's like whenever you have something and you burn it on a piece of leather, it's ingrained there forever like cowhide.

01:47:09.510 --> 01:47:12.270
You brand it.

01:47:12.270 --> 01:47:15.880
Those experiences are branded in my mind.

01:47:28.533 --> 01:47:28.826
They're branded in me.

01:47:39.320 --> 01:47:39.733
They're always there.

01:47:48.428 --> 01:47:49.242
I can recall them.

01:47:54.088 --> 01:47:54.952
My mom said, "Brandon, you always have a memory like an elephant.

01:48:06.982 --> 01:48:07.257
You don't forget nothing.

01:48:24.480 --> 01:48:24.780
" I know, but they truly are there, every single one of them, going to tribulation.

01:48:51.040 --> 01:48:52.225
I can recall them.

01:48:52.225 --> 01:48:56.965
They really happened.

01:48:56.975 --> 01:49:01.793
Every instance is so beautiful, and all the experiences that I've had with the Father.

01:49:01.793 --> 01:49:07.739
I can bring it back—from every angel encounter I've had to the demonic—I don't forget it.

01:49:14.800 --> 01:49:16.080
I remember it, and the Lord shows it to me and I recall it as much as my wedding day.

01:49:21.820 --> 01:49:21.1000
You never forget it.

01:49:21.1000 --> 01:49:28.159
You never forget the day you got born again.

01:49:28.159 --> 01:49:37.430
You never forget the day your first child was born or your children were born.

01:49:37.430 --> 01:49:39.154
You don't forget it.

01:49:39.154 --> 01:49:44.862
When I've seen glimpses of heaven, I'm telling you all, you don't want to miss it.

01:49:44.862 --> 01:49:52.320
He's prepared a place for you that's so beautiful, and he wants you to go so bad.

01:49:52.320 --> 01:49:55.560
And to be absent from the body is to be present with the Lord.

01:49:58.891 --> 01:50:11.131
You know, whenever you almost died giving birth to Paisley, Diana said when she was stepping over and the doctor almost lost her after her C-section, her blood pressure dropped so bad.

01:50:11.131 --> 01:50:19.280
She said, "You tell them what you felt.

01:50:19.280 --> 01:50:30.720
" Whenever it was, it was as easy as—it was easier than anything I've ever experienced in my life.

01:50:30.720 --> 01:50:40.320
It was just like breathing and I felt such a peace, just more peace than I've ever had in my whole life.

01:50:45.085 --> 01:50:45.394
And it was like breathing, like I was there.

01:50:45.394 --> 01:50:52.249
It would have been easier to go than it would have been to stay.

01:50:52.937 --> 01:51:09.966
And I really, really wanted to go because this peace was indescribable, peace on another level that a human can't understand, because the Holy Spirit brings so much peace to us here in this body, in our earthly vessels.

01:51:09.966 --> 01:51:14.391
But whenever I was in that moment, I can't describe it.

01:51:27.599 --> 01:51:30.987
I have no vocabulary to describe it, but it was beautiful and it felt like the way we're supposed to be, like the way we're supposed to feel.

01:51:44.519 --> 01:51:44.799
That peace just makes you feel alive, like this is life.

01:51:44.799 --> 01:51:49.291
It didn't feel like dying; it felt like living.

01:51:51.520 --> 01:51:52.820
I don't know how else to describe it.

01:51:52.820 --> 01:51:54.500
It was beautiful.

01:51:54.500 --> 01:51:57.110
I'll never forget it.

01:52:02.240 --> 01:52:06.068
I have no vocabulary; that's the closest thing I can get to describing it.

01:52:08.061 --> 01:52:11.348
I remember seeing your eyes and I told her, "You're going to lose her.

01:52:11.348 --> 01:52:12.754
She's going.

01:52:14.159 --> 01:52:15.348
" And I could see it.

01:52:27.417 --> 01:52:27.783
I could feel it.

01:52:28.880 --> 01:52:37.480
And I grabbed a hold of your foot and I was praying, "No, you ain't dying on me.

01:52:51.529 --> 01:52:52.359
You ain't dying on me.

01:52:52.359 --> 01:53:02.512
" They rushed in there and she coded, and they brought all their nurses in there to help her.

01:53:09.166 --> 01:53:09.509
I remember thinking, "She's slipping over right now.

01:53:09.509 --> 01:53:13.146
She's leaving me," and they brought her back.

01:53:16.827 --> 01:53:31.406
You know, that in-between, that place where you're about ready to go home—in that instance where Diana was in birth like that and she lost so much blood, it was really scary in the natural for me, but I could see the peace on her face.

01:53:37.760 --> 01:53:37.920
And she said, "Pray for me.

01:53:40.640 --> 01:53:49.074
" And all of a sudden, that was the last thing she said for a second, and she went poof and her eyes got dark.

01:53:49.074 --> 01:53:51.099
I went, "What's going on?

01:54:10.536 --> 01:54:10.800
Is she truly about to die?

01:54:10.800 --> 01:54:16.860
" But they brought her back, all to the glory of God.

01:54:16.860 --> 01:54:17.899
Thank you, Jesus.

01:54:33.900 --> 01:54:34.090
I just try to bring the Lord in these things.

01:54:34.090 --> 01:54:39.520
When he visits and he's talking, I feel his presence so strong right now.

01:54:39.520 --> 01:54:49.794
I want you to realize that he wants a relationship more with you than what you want one with him.

01:54:49.794 --> 01:55:01.440
It's more real, y'all, than what your grandma's preacher told you or whatever.

01:55:01.440 --> 01:55:08.879
Jesus is real and the Holy Spirit is real, and they want a relationship with you.

01:55:08.879 --> 01:55:21.146
He's no respecter of persons; he'll do for you what he does for me and vice versa.

01:55:21.146 --> 01:55:28.800
But he is a respecter of faith and he is a respecter of relationship and time.

01:55:28.800 --> 01:56:49.679
When you die to yourself in time sitting before him, when you lose yourself, there is a level of sacrifice and time.

01:56:49.979 --> 01:56:58.652
How desperate, how hungry, how thirsty are you?

01:56:58.652 --> 01:57:06.040
Is he your every breath?

01:57:06.040 --> 01:57:14.103
Is he as much as you want your next drink of water?

01:57:14.103 --> 01:57:20.879
I'm going to tell you, some days it's not like that for me because the world distracts you.

01:57:20.879 --> 01:57:37.314
This channel, I'm going to tell you, is more distraction than it's ever been in my life.

01:57:37.314 --> 02:01:09.113
Sharing myself with this—if I didn't have this, I know where I'd already be: at my laundry room machine, sitting by my dryer praying, or in my closet, or sitting on the porch talking, looking at the birds.

02:01:09.113 --> 02:01:35.120
I miss those times.

02:01:35.120 --> 02:01:57.943
It's like I said to him last night, "Lord, I'm so tired.

02:01:57.943 --> 02:02:00.192
I'm so thirsty.

02:02:00.192 --> 02:02:08.204
I've dumped out all week and I just need you to help me.

02:02:14.392 --> 02:02:16.229
" I said, "Are you mad at me?

02:02:16.239 --> 02:02:21.040
Is our relationship cooled off out of insecurity?

02:03:00.496 --> 02:03:00.784
" I said, "Lord, are we cool?

02:03:00.784 --> 02:03:02.000
Are we alright?

02:03:02.000 --> 02:03:04.340
" He said, "Brandon, you're tired.

02:03:14.751 --> 02:03:15.778
I'm not mad at you.

02:03:15.778 --> 02:03:25.433
Why would I be mad at you?

02:03:25.433 --> 02:03:27.760
You've helped me, Brandon.

02:03:29.632 --> 02:03:29.920
I want to help you.

02:03:29.920 --> 02:03:33.862
" But I don't want to lose myself in all this.

02:03:33.862 --> 02:03:38.262
You can gain the whole world and lose your soul.

02:03:44.616 --> 02:03:47.610
I don't want to lose my relationship with you because of the people pulling all the time.

02:03:47.610 --> 02:03:59.618
But I understood why the disciples took their time and they gave it away, but at the same time it's so desperate because there's so many people with so many needs.

02:03:59.618 --> 02:04:02.159
There's so many people that are going to hell.

02:04:02.159 --> 02:04:05.531
There's so many people that just don't know.

02:04:07.040 --> 02:04:18.391
And I thought, if I pour myself out and you can pull them out of that pit, if I could help just the 58 of you tonight, I felt like I accomplished something today.

02:04:18.391 --> 02:04:27.403
But there's something to have an authentic relationship with God when you just sit and talk to him.

02:04:33.840 --> 02:04:36.719
And you don't worry about anybody else and what their opinion is because all of it changes like the tide.

02:04:36.719 --> 02:04:51.882
Who cares?

02:04:51.882 --> 02:05:11.040
But there is an authentic move; there's an authentic presence that is tangible.

02:05:50.239 --> 02:05:50.502
And every prayer time is so different here.

02:05:50.502 --> 02:06:20.969
Every time I go, "Well, we'll steer it this way by the Holy Spirit and we'll go there and we'll see what's coming.

02:06:20.969 --> 02:06:26.991
" But every single time is always so different for these people.

02:06:26.991 --> 02:06:33.079
He wants something new for them.

02:06:33.079 --> 02:06:41.256
And I go, "Okay, have your own way, Lord.

02:06:41.256 --> 02:06:43.085
Have your own way.

02:06:43.085 --> 02:06:58.071
You are the potter, we are the clay.

02:06:58.071 --> 02:07:31.880
" You know, it's like the Lord said a lot of times, "The suckers will come, Brandon.

02:07:31.880 --> 02:07:39.640
You'll have to learn the suckers from the authentic people that will try to come in your circle.

02:07:41.379 --> 02:07:53.199
" It's like what Mike said last night, "The higher you go in elevation with ministry, the smaller your circle can be of who's allowed in your inner circle.

02:07:53.199 --> 02:08:01.943
" Because the higher you go, it's like a pyramid.

02:08:01.943 --> 02:08:15.394
He said the smaller the circle, and you have to really realize who is allowed to go in your inner circle.

02:08:15.394 --> 02:08:28.304
Because it was a guy from Rhema that told him that—one of the pastors at Rhema—the bigger the limelight, the bigger the shadow.

02:08:28.304 --> 02:08:39.005
But he was saying about the higher the tip of the pyramid, the smaller the circle is that you allow in your inner circle.

02:08:39.005 --> 02:08:54.409
And I've learned that more and more because you have all kinds of people emailing you.

02:08:54.409 --> 02:09:07.139
You have all kinds of people from different ministries trying to talk to you, and all it really represents is that influence equals money.

02:09:07.139 --> 02:09:34.306
A lot of it the Lord has always said to me: 'If you ever look at My people for money—if you ever do this with the platform that I have given you—it will be no more and the anointing will dry up.

02:09:34.306 --> 02:09:35.290
It'll be dead.

02:09:35.290 --> 02:09:53.805
' He said, 'But if you always seek Me first and bring the people to Me to drink, Brandon, I'll take care of you.

02:09:53.805 --> 02:09:56.182
' And He has.

02:09:56.182 --> 02:10:00.380
But I never seek Him for anything else.

02:10:00.380 --> 02:10:40.066
I always try to keep the authenticity of what I had five years ago before I started this channel: just me, Diana, and the kids praying in the car and doing what we've always done.

02:10:40.066 --> 02:11:01.830
We try to keep the main thing the main thing and bring what we had there here and maintain it.

02:11:01.840 --> 02:12:20.560
That's not always the easiest thing because there's so many people pulling and so many people wanting to talk.

02:12:20.560 --> 02:12:29.173
As I say, y'all, I'm a very private person.

02:12:36.000 --> 02:12:36.297
I don't allow people in my inner circle.

02:12:52.809 --> 02:12:56.869
I just go, 'Okay, I'm leery of it, but I will listen to you.

02:12:56.869 --> 02:13:04.388
' But that's as far as it goes, because if you get through me, you won't get through her.

02:13:04.388 --> 02:13:05.622
It's the truth.

02:13:05.622 --> 02:13:12.900
If you get through my discernment, you won't get through hers.

02:13:12.900 --> 02:13:18.708
She is a pitbull, and I'm telling you, I'm very thankful for that.

02:13:18.708 --> 02:13:21.679
99% of the time, if I miss it, she doesn't.

02:13:21.679 --> 02:13:24.259
I'm going, 'Okay, God, thank God for her.

02:13:24.259 --> 02:13:25.573
' What's the purpose?

02:13:25.573 --> 02:13:26.434
What's the motive?

02:13:26.434 --> 02:13:30.039
A lot of times they say, 'What's the motive?

02:13:30.039 --> 02:13:31.879
What do they want?

02:13:31.879 --> 02:13:35.165
' I can't give you anything that He can't.

02:13:35.165 --> 02:13:36.800
He has it all.

02:13:45.920 --> 02:13:47.579
And if you stay vertical—if you stay vertical and you're looking at Him—everything else horizontal will be taken care of.

02:13:54.140 --> 02:13:54.310
I learned that.

02:13:54.310 --> 02:13:55.000
I'm learning it.

02:13:55.000 --> 02:13:57.211
Nobody else has the answers to fix my issues.

02:13:57.211 --> 02:14:01.869
Now, sometimes I need to talk to somebody: 'Hey, help me.

02:14:01.869 --> 02:14:04.285
I need to learn some wisdom up in here.

02:14:04.285 --> 02:14:11.1000
' But if I stay vertical and don't blow people's texts up, I don't need to figure it out.

02:14:11.1000 --> 02:14:13.471
Just stay vertical.

02:14:13.471 --> 02:14:16.594
Everything else horizontal will be taken care of.

02:14:16.594 --> 02:14:18.272
Brandon can't solve your problems.

02:14:18.272 --> 02:14:21.102
Billy Burke can't solve your problems.

02:14:21.102 --> 02:14:22.799
Pastors can't solve your problems.

02:14:22.799 --> 02:14:23.879
Stay vertical.

02:14:24.986 --> 02:14:28.800
And I've learned that if I do that, everything else falls in line.

02:14:28.800 --> 02:14:30.418
Keep my eyes on Jesus.

02:14:30.418 --> 02:14:34.514
This goes for your marriage, your children, all of it.

02:14:34.514 --> 02:14:35.520
Stay this way.

02:14:55.584 --> 02:14:55.952
We didn't pray very much tonight, did we?

02:14:55.952 --> 02:15:06.099
But we let the Holy Spirit...

02:15:19.093 --> 02:15:19.387
I felt it.

02:15:19.387 --> 02:15:25.760
