02:15:25.760 --> 02:15:33.200
I just want so much for you not to struggle with all the stuff you struggle with.

02:15:33.200 --> 02:15:38.070
There's so many of you that are so broken.

02:15:38.070 --> 02:15:51.551
And I said, 'Lord, how do I help them?

02:15:51.551 --> 02:15:55.439
' He said, 'Bring them to Me.

02:15:55.439 --> 02:15:57.953
I'll fix it.

02:15:57.953 --> 02:15:59.016
You can't.

02:16:15.771 --> 02:16:16.103
There's nothing that you can do, Brandon.

02:16:16.103 --> 02:16:19.835
You're just a man.

02:16:19.835 --> 02:16:31.119
' I said, 'Well, Lord, they ask, but their focus is on You.

02:16:32.388 --> 02:16:32.811
They're going horizontal.

02:16:32.811 --> 02:16:36.286
If they go vertical, I'll fix it all.

02:16:36.286 --> 02:16:38.879
' My marriage is broken.

02:16:38.879 --> 02:16:40.480
'Brandon, help me.

02:16:40.480 --> 02:16:46.160
' My children are strung out.

02:16:46.160 --> 02:16:47.059
Go vertical.

02:16:47.059 --> 02:16:50.960
Go look at Him.

02:16:50.960 --> 02:16:56.008
All I can do is point you to the Father because Brandon is just worthless without Him.

02:16:56.008 --> 02:16:56.108
He is weak and fleshly and has issues just as much as you all.

02:16:56.108 --> 02:16:59.386
And I'm trying to tell you all: if you go vertical and stay on that narrow lane and you keep looking at His face, everything you need is in the Master's face.

02:16:59.386 --> 02:17:04.209
Everything you need is in His beautiful hand, His nail-scarred hand.

02:17:04.209 --> 02:17:08.900
Everything from your healings and deliverances to whatever you think you need.

02:17:08.900 --> 02:17:11.379
Someone may say, 'I need $35,000.

02:17:20.080 --> 02:17:20.297
I need this, I need that.

02:17:20.297 --> 02:17:22.970
' Everything you need is in His hand.

02:17:22.970 --> 02:17:26.880
Lose yourself in Him.

02:17:26.880 --> 02:17:32.399
This world is so poisonous and it's so easy to get lost in it.

02:17:32.399 --> 02:17:35.160
There are so many distractions continually.

02:17:57.679 --> 02:17:58.639
Father, I just thank You, Lord, for tonight.

