02:34:19.552 --> 02:34:28.870
Father, I thank you, Lord, that you're stirring in our nation.

02:34:28.880 --> 02:34:34.272
Father, I know what you told me about Bibi.

02:34:47.724 --> 02:34:50.790
I know what you said about Bibi and what was coming to Bibi, and that the shaking was coming to Israel and everything in Israel would change.

02:34:50.800 --> 02:34:53.874
Everything was going to start to change in Israel.

02:34:56.240 --> 02:35:05.093
